cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically tracking fast moving objects in 6 degrees of freedom and estimating their appearance and pose changes. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves solving a reconstruction problem, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics). The dataset generation involves high-speed camera recordings, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the method involves simultaneous estimation of multiple parameters, which could involve machine learning techniques and fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
